OpenCode OpenAI Proxy v2
OpenAI-compatible proxy for OpenCode API

Improvements over v1:
  - Session caching with LRU eviction & TTL-based cleanup
  - Full conversation history preservation
  - Accurate token counting via tiktoken
  - Per-session SSE event isolation (/session/:id/event)
  - Concurrency limiting
  - Enhanced error handling and structured logging
"""

